        "translation": "Nor is it far from human.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b03_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "湛然寂靜。",
        "translation": "They are perfectly tranquil.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b03_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "只在自己性中。",
        "translation": "It's only in their own nature.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b03_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但以自己性智慧。",
        "translation": "He simply uses the wisdom of his own nature.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b04_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "照破諸妄。",
        "translation": "He illuminates and refutes delusions.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b04_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則曉然自見。",
        "translation": "Then he clearly sees for himself.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b04_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故大般若經六百卷。",
        "translation": "That's why there are six hundred fascicles of the Mahāprajñāpāramitā-sūtra.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆如來為菩薩果人。",
        "translation": "Each one is written by the Tathāgata for a person who's the fruit of bodhisattvahood.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b05_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說佛性。",
        "translation": "They explain the buddha-nature.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b05_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然而其間。",
        "translation": "Yet, there are still some of them.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b06_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶有為頓漸者說。",
        "translation": "There are still some that are explained for those who are gradual and sudden.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b06_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟金剛經。",
        "translation": "Only the Diamond Sutra.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b06_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為發大乘者說。",
        "translation": "It's taught for those who give rise to the great vehicle.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b06_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為發最上乘者說。",
        "translation": "It's taught for those who give rise to the supreme vehicle.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b07_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故其經。",
        "translation": "That's why the sūtra says.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b07_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先說四生四相。",
        "translation": "First, it explains the four births and four phases.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b07_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次云凡所有相。",
        "translation": "Next, it says that all marks are false.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b07_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆是虗妄。",
        "translation": "They're all false and illusory.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b08_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若見諸相非相。",
        "translation": "If we see that the marks are not marks, then we'll see the Tathāgata.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b08_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即見如來。",
        "translation": "That's when you see the Tathāgata.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b08_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盖顯一切法。",
        "translation": "This is a way to show that all dharmas ...",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b08_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至無所住。",
        "translation": "Up to now, they have no abode.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b09_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為真諦。",
        "translation": "This is the true truth.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b09_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故如來於此經。",
        "translation": "That's why the Tathāgata explains this sūtra.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b09_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡說涉有即破之。",
        "translation": "Whenever it's said to involve existence, it's rejected.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b09_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以非直取實相。",
        "translation": "It's because it doesn't directly grasp the true nature.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b10_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以示眾生。",
        "translation": "It's to show sentient beings.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b10_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盖恐眾生不解佛所說。",
        "translation": "That's because he's afraid that sentient beings won't understand what the Buddha teaches.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b10_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其心反有所住故也。",
        "translation": "Their minds might instead have some abiding.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b11_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所謂佛法即非佛法之類是也。",
        "translation": "This is the sort of thing that's called a Buddhist teaching that's not a Buddhist teaching.",
        "source": "X24n0460_001:0535b11_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
